  "texts": [
    "Dependence of the loss function as a function of epoch number obtained during the evaluation process for the binary classifier using the test dataset (A) or the training dataset (B).",
    "Series in each figure corresponds to the number of datapoints in the augmentation dataset.",
    "Initially, both losses were at same point (approximately 0.67) and then they start to diverge as the epoch number increases, reaching the maximum difference at epoch #40.",
    "At this point, the model was considered to be overfitted and thus provided a rather poor generalization of unseen data.",
    "In contrast, the classifier trained only with 5 epochs was underfitted."
  ],
